According by John Maxwell, one analyst for Wheat First Securities, Richmond, Va, Benson & Hedges, e don fall from 4.7% of di cigarette market for 1985 to just 4.1% after second quarter of dis year.

Di brand name na No. 7 overall for di cigarette business, Mr. Maxwell yarn.

Di slip don come despite high profile advert wey Wells Rich make, one picture wey young man just dey clap for inside pajama bottom dey interrupt one special brunch.

Dat one wey e do come generate plenty publicity sotay one trade magazine launch contest wey people go dey to see who di guy be, and wetin e dey do.

